## Original version

windows-bg-notifications-title-a = New Firefox. More private. Fewer trackers. No compromises.
windows-bg-notifications-body-a = Try the newest Firefox now, upgraded with our strongest anti-tracking protection yet.
windows-bg-notifications-open-button-a = Open Firefox now
windows-bg-notifications-remind-button-a = Remind me later

## Variant (the buttons remain the same)

windows-bg-notifications-title-b = Firefox is now faster than ever
# “minus the lag” refers to reducing the presence of “lag” in the user experience.
# Alternative versions: "Multiple tabs, no lag" or "Multiple tabs without the lag".
windows-bg-notifications-title-c = Speedy page load times. Multiple tabs, minus the lag. Doesn’t waste memory so other programs run at top speed.
